Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【製作名單】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}片源提供:{\fscx90}Zhq
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}對白翻譯:呆呆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}對白校對:灰 Edge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}繁體校正:空心之人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}字幕計時:吉祥如意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}後期製作:{\fscx90}MR Yaha
